TeraAI tells you if you are correct and explains what you missed.

00:06:49.999 --> 00:06:53.999
This turns a passive reading session into an active conversation.

00:06:53.999 --> 00:06:57.999
The difference is dramatic.

00:06:57.999 --> 00:07:01.999
When you answer a question, your brain has to retrieve the information.

00:07:01.999 --> 00:07:05.999
That retrieval process strengthens the neural pathways.

00:07:05.999 --> 00:07:09.999
It transforms short term understanding into long term memory.

00:07:09.999 --> 00:07:13.999
It also gives you immediate feedback on what you actually understood versus what you just skimmed.

00:07:13.999 --> 00:07:17.999
No more false confidence from re-reading without comprehension.

00:07:17.999 --> 00:07:21.999
Testing yourself makes the session active.

00:07:21.999 --> 00:07:25.999
It wakes your brain up and helps you remember.

00:07:25.999 --> 00:07:28.692
Sometimes even the small start feels too hard.

00:07:28.692 --> 00:07:31.384
