00:08:11.769 --> 00:08:14.461
Until your brain finally says: yes, I can do that.

00:08:14.461 --> 00:08:17.153
The goal is not to study perfectly.

00:08:17.153 --> 00:08:19.846
The goal is to study at all.

00:08:19.846 --> 00:08:22.538
Even one minute of focused learning is better than none.

00:08:22.538 --> 00:08:25.230
Even understanding one concept is a win.

00:08:25.230 --> 00:08:27.923
Progress is not linear.

00:08:27.923 --> 00:08:30.615
Some days you will study for an hour.

